{"ID":"20260528192530-av71gs8","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260528192530-av71gs8","title":"2023年全国甲卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605101017"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192556-33gb2l6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192556-33gb2l6","updated":"20260528192556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"随着中国考古学的飞速发展，考古资料得以大量积累，考古学文化时空框架体系基本建立，多学科合作日益深入，各种专题研究广泛展开。“考古写史”在中国已经取得巨大成就，获得诸多具有突破性和填补空白意义的成绩，中国考古学证明了自身的价值，尤其是在上古史构建方面展现了广阔前景。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192556-sfgje9n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192556-sfgje9n","updated":"20260528192556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从考古发现来看，考古学提供了传统历史学不可想象的新发现、新材科，呈现出不同时期的古代物质文化面貌、古人日常生产生活状态以及各地的文明化进程等，如不同区域新石器时代晚期大型聚落遗址、大型公共建筑、大型墓葬、水利设施、手工业作坊，以及象征王权、神权、军权和复杂礼制出现的精美玉器、陶器、漆器、象牙器等。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192556-yd0rxie","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192556-yd0rxie","updated":"20260528192556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从重构上古史体系角度看，20世纪70—80年代，夏鼐、苏秉琦等系统地构建了新石器与夏商周三代时期的考古学文化区系类型时空框架体系。苏秉琦在新石器时代考古学文化区系类型基础上提出“满天星斗”“多元一体”和“古国一方国帝国”等关于中国上古史的历史叙述体系。严文明提出“重瓣花朵”模式，在承认多区域文化共存的文化多元性的同时，强调中原文化区“联系各文化区的核心作用”。张光直认为各地区文化多元发展并通过彼此之间的密切交流而形成一个“中国相互作用圈”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192556-v6rxfsm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192556-v6rxfsm","updated":"20260528192556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从二里头文化、二里岗文化到殷墟考古学文化、周代考古学文化，考古学不仅展现了不同于传统文献记载的这一时期文化、科技、礼制等众多方面从发展到成熟的历史脉络，而且填补了诸多传统历史学的空白，如四川的三星堆——金沙文化、江西的吴城文化、两周时期的曾国与中山国历史，等等。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192556-6akrtlv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192556-6akrtlv","updated":"20260528192556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这些成果证明考古学完全有能力担当重写中国上古史的重任，并且已经初步形成具有自身特色的上古史叙述与解释体系，超越了传统的具有传说性质的三皇五帝体系和存在争议的夏商周三代古史体系，正如习近平总书记所说：“经过几代考古人接续奋斗，我国考古工作取得了重大成就，延伸了历史轴线，增强了历史信度，丰富了历史内涵，活化了历史场景。”"}]},{"ID":"20260528192556-lk3dzsb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192556-lk3dzsb","updated":"20260528192556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学界一直存在着“证经补史”的传统史学思路，试图将考古学文化体系纳入三皇五帝的古史框架体系之中，似乎中国考古学如果没有发现并证明三皇五帝与夏商周，就没有价值和意义，但研究实践告诉我们：这种传统治史思路影响了中国考古学的视野和思维方式，限制了考古学在重构中国上古史中的作用。比如，考古发现与研究显示，二里头遗址和二里头文化在东亚地区的文明形成与发展中占据了关键性地位，奠定了中国独特的礼乐文化传统的基础，在人类文明史上具有世界性的标志意义，尽管二里头遗址是否就是文献记载中的夏都所在地，在学术界仍有争议。我们对二里头遗址与二里头文化应该开展扎实的田野工作并展开全方位的考古学研究与阐释，而不是将主要目标集中于它是否是文献记载中的“夏”，并为此争论不休。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192556-gmq6plx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192556-gmq6plx","updated":"20260528192556"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（摘编自徐良高《以考古学构建中国上古史》）"}]},{"ID":"20260528192530-2qlm1nz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528192530-2qlm1nz","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-kenr5r5","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-kenr5r5","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192610-4vk9ogy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-4vk9ogy","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192610-tl5zry6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-tl5zry6","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下列关于原文内容的理解和分析，正确的一项是（   ）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-gtg2ycr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-gtg2ycr","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. 考古学者对新石器时代的考古，更侧重发掘能体现古代物质文化面貌的大型遗址。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-9nl67gd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-9nl67gd","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 考古发现可以为有文献记载的历史提供参考、印证和补充，让历史的内涵更丰富。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-nq092s5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-nq092s5","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 考古证明，“证经补史”的传统史学思路，很难为中国上古史提供叙述与解释体系。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-vonxy06","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-vonxy06","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. 二里头遗址是否就是文献记载中的夏都无关紧要，紧要的是开展更为扎实的研究。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-x9jbfgb","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-x9jbfgb","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192610-6ahttk4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-6ahttk4","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192610-m0yf1qd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-m0yf1qd","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下列对原文论证的相关分析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-q9438ek","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-q9438ek","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. 文章开宗明义，然后从不同角度论述中国考古学能担当重写中国上古史的重任。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-8fcmamj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-8fcmamj","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 文章在展开论述时，注重将传统历史学作为参照，用以凸显考古学的独特价值。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-79elg5u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-79elg5u","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 第二段和第四段列举诸多考古发现，是为了证明考古学具有延伸历史轴线的功能。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-ji4ml6p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-ji4ml6p","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. 第三段介绍多种学术观点，展示了考古学在上古史体系构建方面取得的丰硕成果。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-w6489l6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-w6489l6","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192610-cc8gdwc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-cc8gdwc","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192610-1wocc5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-1wocc5c","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据原文内容，下列说法不正确的一项是（   ）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-tcfk4mg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-tcfk4mg","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. 出土的精美玉器、陶器、漆器、象牙器等，能为其所属时期的文明化进程提供佐证。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-o74i1bw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-o74i1bw","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 中国考古学的众多研究成果证明，“三皇五帝”只是神话传说，而非实有其人。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-2i15qyn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-2i15qyn","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 在二里头遗址和二里头文化中，已经发现了有关中华文明礼乐文化的信息。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192610-m0qgowf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192610-m0qgowf","updated":"20260528192610"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. “考古写史”立足于考古发现，与以文献为本位的“证经补史”研究路径不同。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192530-tobbguk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528192530-tobbguk","updated":"20260528192623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260528192623-0i8pzmn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192623-0i8pzmn","updated":"20260528192623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192623-fz8txha","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528192623-fz8txha","updated":"20260528192623"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528192623-ahcip8s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192623-ahcip8s","updated":"20260528192623"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C    2. C    3. B"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528192530-jb1mij4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528192530-jb1mij4","updated":"20260605101013"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-hvg458n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-hvg458n","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【1题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-dsy8jur","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-dsy8jur","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生理解分析文章内容的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-dflb0dh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-dflb0dh","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“……更侧重发掘能体现古代物质文化面貌的大型遗址”错误，文中说的是“如不同区域新石器时代晚期大型聚落遗址、大型公共建筑、大型墓葬、水利设施、手工业作坊，以及象征王权、神权、军权和复杂礼制出现的精美玉器、陶器、漆器、象牙器等”，“以及”表示并列，无法看出侧重哪方面。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-9tazale","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-9tazale","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“考古发现可以为……”错误，张冠李戴，由文中“考古学提供了……”“考古学不仅展现了……而且填补了……”可知，是“考古学”，而非“考古发现”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-azl09dz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-azl09dz","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“二里头遗址是否就是文献记载中的夏都无关紧要”错误，文章最后一段说的是“我们对二里头遗址与二里头文化应该开展扎实的田野工作并展开全方位的考古学研究与阐释，而不是将主要目标集中于它是否是文献记载中的‘夏’……”，文中是说不能将主要目标集中于“它是否是文献记载中的‘夏’”，并非“无关紧要”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-dv0nf3z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-dv0nf3z","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-g9eqofu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-g9eqofu","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【2题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-1n366es","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-1n366es","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生分析论据、论点以及论证的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-q5aaa10","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-q5aaa10","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“是为了证明考古学具有延伸历史轴线的功能”错误，第二段和第四段列举诸多考古发现，第五段开头用“这些成果证明考古学完全有能力担当重写中国上古史的重任，并且已经初步形成具有自身特色的上古史叙述与解释体系，超越……古史体系”进行了总结，由此可知，列举这些考古发现的目的是为了证明“中国考古学能担当重写中国上古史的重任”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-m2q6ib2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-m2q6ib2","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-sr6ihql","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-sr6ihql","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【3题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-41rm8uk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-41rm8uk","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生理解文章信息，把握作者观点态度的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-k11cebf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-k11cebf","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“中国考古学的众多研究成果证明，‘三皇五帝’只是神话传说，而非实有其人”错误，文中说的是“这些成果证明考古学……超越了传统的具有传说性质的三皇五帝体系”“似乎中国考古学如果没有发现并证明三皇五帝与夏商周”，文中只是说“超越了”“具有传说性质的三皇五帝体系”，并没有说就此证明其“只是神话传说，而非实有其人”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192645-t69xen5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192645-t69xen5","updated":"20260528192645"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260528192530-b3yeht2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192530-b3yeht2","updated":"20260605101013"}},{"ID":"20260528192829-dn2mapz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528192829-dn2mapz","updated":"20260528192829"}}]}